1
00:00:01,200 --> 00:00:03,240
(DOCTOR WHO THEME)

2
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Who the hell are you?

3
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:09,840
I'm you, from your future.

4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:12,160
Tell me exactly what's happened.

5
00:00:12,440 --> 00:00:16,000
Well, the exterior shell of the Tardis
has drifted forwards in time.

6
00:00:16,080 --> 00:00:18,400
If you step into the box now,

7
00:00:18,480 --> 00:00:21,000
you step inside the control room
a tiny bit into the past.

8
00:00:21,640 --> 00:00:22,760
I don't understand.

9
00:00:23,120 --> 00:00:24,120
Neither do I.

10
00:00:24,640 --> 00:00:25,640
You just said it.

11
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:26,960
No, I'm just repeating it.

12
00:00:27,360 --> 00:00:28,960
I'm just remembering
what I heard myself saying

13
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:30,160
when I was standing where you are now.

14
00:00:30,240 --> 00:00:33,360
And repeating it. I'm just
repeating this, too. And this. And this.

15
00:00:33,680 --> 00:00:34,800
Oh, I still don't understand.

16
00:00:35,080 --> 00:00:37,120
-You still don't.
-Okay, when does this Amy

17
00:00:37,200 --> 00:00:39,120
step inside the box?
We need to maintain the timeline.

18
00:00:39,240 --> 00:00:40,840
Ah! As soon as she's slapped Rory.

19
00:00:41,240 --> 00:00:44,000
-Okay.
-Ha! No. Why do I get slapped?

20
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:45,960
Because we have to stick to the
established chain of events.

21
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:47,920
One mistake and the whole timeline
could collapse.

22
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:50,880
We'll end up with two Amy Ponds
forever, and then what would you do?

23
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:55,000
-Oh!
-Okay, you,

24
00:00:55,080 --> 00:00:56,720
into the police box now.

25
00:00:57,440 --> 00:00:59,960
-What, and then I become her?
-Yes, go, go, go!

26
00:01:01,440 --> 00:01:02,840
Do I really look like that?

27
00:01:02,920 --> 00:01:04,520
Yeah. Yeah, you do.

28
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:06,360
Oh! I'd give you a driving license.

29
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:10,240
-Mmm, I bet you would.
-Oh, this is how it all ends.

30
00:01:10,320 --> 00:01:13,040
Pond flirting with herself,
true love at last.

31
00:01:14,000 --> 00:01:17,520
-Oh, sorry, Rory.
-Absolutely no problem at all.

32
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,920
-Now, Amy!
-What's the first line?

33
00:01:20,080 --> 00:01:21,960
"Okay, kids,
this is where it gets complicated.”

34
00:01:22,080 --> 00:01:23,240
Gotcha!

35
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:26,800
-So, is that it? Are we okay now?
-No, we're still trapped.

36
00:01:30,640 --> 00:01:32,720
-What are you doing?
-You told us to get into the police box.

37
00:01:33,320 --> 00:01:34,560
Well, from your point of view,

38
00:01:34,640 --> 00:01:36,160
you're about to tell us
to get into the police box.

39
00:01:36,240 --> 00:01:39,200
From our point of view, you just told us
to get into the police box, which is

40
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:42,560
why we got into the police box,
which is why we're here.

41
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,040
Do I have to remember all of that?

42
00:01:44,120 --> 00:01:45,840
-It sort of happens.
-Hi.

43
00:01:46,120 --> 00:01:47,680
-Hi.
-Hey, stop that.

44
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:49,880
You two, into the police box now, run.

45
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,920
-So, what now?
-You two, stay where you are.

46
00:01:53,160 --> 00:01:54,160
What are you doing?

47
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,760
I'm setting up a
controlled temporal implosion.

48
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,960
It's the only way to reset the Tardis,

49
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:59,680
but unless I find exactly the right
lever to control the implosion,

50
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:01,520
we're all going to die.

51
00:02:01,720 --> 00:02:03,480
You don't know which lever?

52
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:06,400
Well, no, but I'm about to find out.

53
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:09,520
-(GASPS)
-The wibbly lever.

54
00:02:09,640 --> 00:02:11,800
The wibbly lever, thank you!

55
00:02:16,760 --> 00:02:18,320
(WHOOSHING)

56
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:33,720
Okay, we're back in normal flight.
The Tardis is no longer inside itself,

57
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,680
the localised time field
is no longer about to implode

58
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:38,520
and rip a hole in all causality,
but just in case,

59
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:42,280
Pond, put some trousers on.

